H0.text: In Greek mythology, what was the name of the nymph who fell in love with Narcissus, but who was said to have pined away when her love was not returned, leaving only her voice. Daphne

H1.text: In Greek mythology, what was the name of the nymph who fell in love with Narcissus, but who was said to have pined away when her love was not returned, leaving only her voice. Calliope

H2.text: In Greek mythology, what was the name of the nymph who fell in love with Narcissus, but who was said to have pined away when her love was not returned, leaving only her voice. Galatea

H3.text: In Greek mythology, what was the name of the nymph who fell in love with Narcissus, but who was said to have pined away when her love was not returned, leaving only her voice. Echo

A4.text: Hera made her only able to speak the last words spoken to her.

A5.text: Eventually, Echo, too, began to waste away.
